EAST SIBERIAN SEA.
LAPTEV SEA.
1. VESSEL, GREEN HULL, ONE PERSON ON BOARD,
   DISABLED AND ADRIFT IN AREA BOUND BY
   73-20.4N 139-52.9E, 72-29.0N 139-36.0E,
   72-36.0N 144-46.0E, 73-12.2N 143-34.3E.
   VESSELS IN VICINITY REQUESTED TO KEEP A
   SHARP LOOKOUT, ASSIST IF POSSIBLE.
   REPORTS TO ANY COASTAL RADIO STATION.
2. CANCEL HYDROARC 166/14.
